(9, 4, 'Small Machine Room Elevator', 'コンパクトな機械室のエレベーター', 'small-machine-room-elevator', 'storage/images/product/9/1700035890259778.jpg', 'Small volume traction machine combines with an integrated controller, so that it makes the machine room size the same as well size. It covers the equal area as that of the well. At the same time of reducing the machine room height it beautifies the building outlook. It fulfills super small standards of machine room space and building cost.', '小さな荷物を運ぶエレベーターは、統合制御システムと組み合わせて、適切なサイズの機械室を持つようにし、あなたの家をより美しくする。乗客エレベーターは非常に小さな最上階の高さだけを必要とし、建設コストも高くない。', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/c&oacute; ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y ảnh 1.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"626\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Small Machine Room Elevator Construction Sketch</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/c&oacute; ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y drawing.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1016\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Specification</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/c&oacute; ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y th&ocirc;ng số.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"781\" /></strong></p>', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/c&oacute; ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y ảnh nhật.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"622\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>小型機械室エレベーター建設スケッチ</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/c&oacute; ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y drawing2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1016\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>仕様書</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/c&oacute; ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y th&ocirc;ng số nhật.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"802\" /></p>', 1, '2023-11-01 22:52:04', '2023-11-14 23:11:30'),
(10, 4, 'Machine Room-less Elevator', '部屋のないエレベーター', 'machine-room-less-elevator', 'storage/images/product/10/1700035719728492.jpg', 'FUJI machine room-less elevator series resolves the restriction to the elevator in the construction, building cost, building design style, use range. At the same time of saving the space and cost, it provides the passengers with upper level intellectual, effective and stable travel.', 'FUJIのエレベーターの機械室のないモデルは、建設、建設費用、建物のデザインスタイル、利用範囲に関する制約を克服する。同時にスペースとコストを節約し、乗客にスマートで効率的かつ安定した移動を提供する。', '<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/k ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y ảnh 1.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"562\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Machine Room-less Elevator Construction Sketch</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/K PH&Ograve;NG M&Aacute;Y DRAWING.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1137\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Specification</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số k ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"433\" /></strong></p>', '<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/k ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y ảnh nhật.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"592\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>機械室レスエレベーターの構造スケッチ</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/k ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y drawing 2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1161\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>仕様書</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/k ph&ograve;ng m&aacute;y th&ocirc;ng số nhật.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"434\" /></strong></p>', 1, '2023-11-01 23:07:11', '2023-11-14 23:08:39'),
(11, 5, 'Gearless Traction Machine FJG09', 'エレベーターギヤレス巻上機 FJG09', 'gearless-traction-machine-fjg09', 'storage/images/product/11/1699944517047604.jpg', 'Rated load: 630-1000kg\r\nRated speed: 1.0-2.0m/s\r\nSuspension: 2:1', '定格荷重:630-1000kg\r\n定格速度: 1.0-2.0m/s\r\nサスペンション: 2:1', '<p><strong>FEATURE</strong></p>\r\n<p>- Special housing design provides stable and high structural rigidity. Design is verified FEM and physical mechanical test.</p>\r\n<p>- Designed by outer rotor. Possible to generate bigger torque with low noise and vibration. Provides a comfortable ride.</p>\r\n<p>- Solid construction for permissible shaft load Fs at the traction sheave up to 35kN</p>\r\n<p>- Safety brake system with electro-magnetical release, provides min. 2x950Nm</p>\r\n<p>- Groove profiles according to lift system</p>\r\n<p>- Perfect rated motor, use of high-performance permanent magnet, degree of protection IP40, insulation class 155&deg;C (F), temperature control</p>\r\n<p>-Motor with 2 times overload capacity; max. traveling height up to 120m</p>\r\n<p>- EC type-examination certificate according to EN 81-20/50, can be used for UCM solution</p>\r\n<p>- Inverter compatible measuring device, rigid coupling or integrated. (e.g. ECN 1313; ERN 1387; TS5213N2503; EI53C9.25-2048-SA5N2T)</p>\r\n<p>- Variable options regarding voltage, speed, torque, braking torque and traction sheave parameters</p>\r\n<p>- The braker passed 2 million times braking. After the test, its performance is still in specification. Safety is guaranteed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>DIMENSION DRAWING</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/Catalog-Japan-20237_0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"831\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATION</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/E-_Mr-Tu_Scan_Mr-Tu_Catalog-Japan-2023_Catalog-Japan-2022-Folder_View-2023_Catalog-Japan-20236a_07.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"403\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../stor