(17, 4, 'High Speed Elevator', '高速エレベーター', 'high-speed-elevator', 'storage/images/product/17/1700035593201507.jpg', 'A shock-absorbing device is set between the car body and holder to isolate vibration. It superiorly buffers vibration during the elevator running process. It reduces the car vibration and prompts the conformable travel to vast passengers. The combined car wall connection ensures mute effects in the car, the stable and enclosed air pressure.', 'ショックアブソーバー装置は、エレベーターキャビンとガイドレールの間に取り付けられ、振動を防ぐ。これにより、エレベーターの運転中に車両の振動が軽減され、大勢の乗客に適している。キャビン壁の結合は、内部で騒音を抑制し、空気圧力を一定に保つことを確実にする。', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/tốc độ cao ảnh 1.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"346\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>High Speed Elevator Construction Sketch</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/tốc độ cao drawing.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1145\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Specification</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số tốc độ cao.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"616\" /></strong></p>', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/tốc độ cao ảnh 2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"332\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>高速エレベーター建設スケッチ</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/tốc độ cao drawing 2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1222\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>仕様</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số tốc độ cao 2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"618\" /></strong></p>', 1, '2023-11-07 22:52:42', '2023-11-14 23:06:33'),
(18, 6, 'Cargo Elevator', 'カーゴエレベーター', 'cargo-elevator', 'storage/images/product/18/1700035537352593.jpg', 'A freight elevator is a means of transporting goods vertically. It is a very important part of factories, warehouses, warehouses in buildings, libraries... with the ability to withstand loads. high, able to withstand impact and transport heavy goods quickly, durable and effectively.', '貨物用エレベーターは、荷物を垂直に輸送する手段です。 工場、倉庫、ビル倉庫、図書館などにおいて、耐荷重性が求められる非常に重要な部品です。 高く、衝撃に耐え、重量物を素早く、耐久性があり、効果的に輸送できます。', '<p><strong>* Loading giants that can release more and more cargo pressure for you</strong></p>\r\n<p>FUJI freight lift serial fully utilizes the advanced and fully computerized control technology. It employs the well-developed WWVFcontrol system of FUJI elevator. It is sample in structure and convenient in repair and maintenance. It fulfills a qualitative leap in the aspects of the signal transmission and running control. It brings about the more stable and reliable system, the lower noise, the smoother running, the more accurate leveling. It is more and more easy for goods to enter and exit. In addition, FUJI freight lift series can offer the microprocessor. The high speed running capabilities and expansion interface ensure to satisfy the special requirements from broad users.</p>\r\n<p><strong>* Light curtain protection</strong></p>\r\n<p>Several protective light curtains are formed at the entrance of the elevator, which sensibly detects and responses to any objects that intrude into the detecting scope. The safety of humans and cargoes are guaranteed.</p>\r\n<p><strong>* Very humane operation</strong></p>\r\n<p>It is equipped with a fully automatic collective selective function. It can fulfill operation with driver/without driver. The operation box specially and additionally sets\" door-shut delay button in the operation box. Door-shut delay time can be flexibly adjusted at site according to the requirements. You feel more at ease when loading and unloading the goods o