(19, 7, 'Home Elevator', '家庭用エレベーター', 'home-elevator', 'storage/images/product/19/1700035437138280.jpg', 'Home elevators are suitable for homes with small areas. They have much less frequency of use than passenger elevators but require high reliability, precision, absolute safety and energy saving.', 'ホームエレベーターは面積が狭い家に適しています。 旅客用エレベーターに比べて使用頻度ははるかに低いですが、高い信頼性、精度、絶対的な安全性、省エネ性が求められます。', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Your perfect life is comfortable and relax</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The humanization design decorates your noble life space. We enhance your life grade in the times of high &amp; new tech. FUJI home elevator brings about a more convenient and high-grade life.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">It displays the outstanding properties in a limited space. It has no machine room. Extremely small top-floor height can match with various old and new residences. Relying on the standard track installation system, the elevator can be installed more quickly and conveniently. In addition, the smooth start and leveling system bring about the rare stable elevator operation. Therefore you feel more comfortable in the elevator.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Characteristics of home elevators</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">*No need for a traditional machine room, without any construc- tion cost increased. Specially designed rucksack frame for the home elevator with traction ratio 2:1 VVVF drive technology, FUJI home elevator appropriate micro processing control.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">*Slide + roller composite guide shoe.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">*The appropriate traction machine bracket is fixed on the guide rail.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The building will not have any load.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">*We apply 220V single-phase home elevator special machine.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">*Automatic special door machine,synchronous timing belt transmission,TUV CE Certification passed.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Home elevator construction sketch</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/bản vẽ thang home.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1218\" /></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><strong>Specification</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang home.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"184\" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-139e7861-7fff-d682-7ea4-2baf9bab804e\"></span></p>', '<p><strong>完璧な生活は快適でリラックスしています</strong></p>\r\n<p>ヒューマンセンスのデザインが貴族の生活空間の雰囲気を飾り立てる。高度で新しいテクノロジーの時代において、私たちはあなたの生活の質を向上させる。FUJIの家庭用エレベーターは、より便利で高級な生活をもたらす。</p>\r\n<p>このエレベーターは限られたスペースで優れた特性を示す。機械室がなく、極めて小さな最上階の高さは、さまざまな古い住宅や新しい住宅に合致する。標準のトラック取り付けシステムに依存することで、エレベーターをより迅速かつ便利に取り付けることができる。さらに、スムーズな始動とレベリングシステムにより、稀に見る安定したエレベーターの運転を実現している。したがって、エレベーター内でより快適に感じることができる。</p>\r\n<p><strong>家庭用エレベーターの特徴</strong></p>\r\n<p>* 伝統的な機械室が不要で、建設コストは増加しない。牽引比2:1 VVVF駆動技術を備えた家庭用エレベーター向けに特別に設計されたリュックサックフレーム、FUJI家庭用エレベーターに適切なマイクロプロセッシング制御を採用している。</p>\r\n<p>* スライド+ローラー複合ガイドシュー。</p>\r\n<p>* 適切な牽引機のブラケットがガイドレールに固定される。建物に負荷がかからない。</p>\r\n<p>* 220V単相家庭用エレベーター専用機を採用している。</p>\r\n<p>* 自動特殊ドア機、同期タイミングベルト伝動、TUV CE認証を取得している。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>家庭用エレベーター建設スケッチ</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/bản vẽ thang home 2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1218\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang home 2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"188\" /></strong></p>', 1, '2023-11-07 23:55:28', '2023-11-14 23:03:57'),
(20, 8, 'Hospital Elevator', '病院用エレベーター', 'hospital-elevator', 'storage/images/product/20/1700035287595900.jpg', 'Hospital elevators are considered a necessary means, effectively supporting timely movement to serve patients.', '病院のエレベーターは、患者にサービスを提供するためのタイムリーな移動を効果的にサポートする必要な手段と考えられています。', '<p>FUJI hospital elevators are not just used in delivering passengers. Because of its use particularity, it has special and strict requirements to the elevator use properties. FUJI hospital elevator can accurately control the elevators\' running speed. It brings about smooth and comfortable travel.</p>\r\n<p>FUJI hospital elevator lays special importance upon the humane design. It fully optimizes the car structure. It satisfies the clients\' use requirements to the greatest extent. It creates a peaceful and graceful space for vast passengers.</p>\r\n<p>FUJI hospital elevator satisfies the needs of emergency patients\' delivery. It applies humanization design and is equipped with a full set of top equipment. It is smooth and comfortable to run in.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hospital Elevator Construction Sketch</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/bv thang bệnh viện.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1123\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Specification</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang bệnh viện.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"261\" /></strong></p>', '<p>FUJIの病院用エレベーターは、乗客を輸送するためだけでなく、特定の要件が厳格であるため、使用時に特別な要求を持っている。FUJIの病院用エレベーターは、正確な運行速度を制御でき、スムーズで快適な移動を提供する。</p>\r\n<p>FUJIの病院用エレベーターはスマートな設計を特に重視している。それは車両の構造を最適化し、顧客の要求を最大限に満たしている。それは快適で居心地の良いスペースを提供し、多くの乗客の輸送ニーズに応えている。</p>\r\n<p>FUJIの病院用エレベーターは、緊急時の患者の輸送ニーズに応える。それはスマートなデザインを採用し、トップクラスの設備を完備し、非常に静かで快適に動作できる。</p>\r\n<p><strong>病院のエレベーター建設のスケッチ</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/bv thang bệnh viện 2.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1128\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>仕様</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang bệnh viện nhật.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"273\" /></strong></p>', 1, '2023-11-08 23:22:10', '2023-11-14 23:01:27'),
(21, 9, 'Semicircle Observation Elevator', '半円形展望エレベーター', 'semicircle-observation-elevator', 'storage/images/product/21/1700035208527716.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong>Excellent car wall</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">It adopts highly secure, safety laminated glass. It is transparent. The passengers might appreciate the busy and prosperous city sight through the transparent car wall. The Laminated layer in laminated glass resists radiation. It buffers sound-wave vibration and isolates the sound. Large area car wall glass design shows smooth and beautiful lines. It beautifies the elevator car outline. Furthermore, the buildings are attractive.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong>Super wide field of view</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Full transparent lift car design can maximize the field of view. Through the visual extension, passengers can have a panoramic view of all the beautiful scenery.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong>Multiple lift car shapes</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Round,square and rhombic and other lift car shapes are optional, perfectly corresponding to different architectural styles.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong>Outer glass hood</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">It harmoniously combines with the building and surroundings. Panoramic elevator is part of the building. It also adds a mobile charming scene for the building.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong>Excellent sound insulation</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">The structure of the lift car is further optimized, which facilitates the elevator to achieve excellent sound insulation effect and customers to have quiet and steady using experience.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong>Diverse decorative designs</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">There are a series of optional materials and colors for hoistway doors, handles and lift car walls, thus truly realizing individualized customized services.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Semicircle Observation Elevator Construction Sketch</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/drawing thang k&iacute;nh tr&ograve;n.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1006\" /></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Specification</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang k&iacute;nh tr&ograve;n.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"542\" /></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a16fb005-7fff-7507-646e-17dccc2c27bf\"></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">優れたカーウォール</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">このウオールは安全強化ガラスを採用している。ウオール自体は透明であるので、乗客は透明なカーウォールを通じて賑やかで繁華な都市の景色を楽しむことができる。積層ガラスの中の積層層は放射線に対抗する。音波振動を緩衝し、音を遮断する効果も整えている。広いエリアのカーウォールガラスデザインは、滑らかで美しいラインを示し、エレベーターカーの輪郭を美化する。さらに、建物は魅力的である。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">超広い視野</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">完全透明のリフトカーのデザインは、視野を最大化できる。視覚の拡張を通じて、乗客は美しい景色のパノラマビューを楽しむことができる。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">複数のリフトカーの形状</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">円形、四角形、ひし形など、さまざまなリフトカーの形状が選択可能で、異なる建築スタイルに完璧に対応している。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">外部ガラスフード</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">建物と周囲と調和している。パノラマエレベーターは建物の一部である。建物に移動中の魅力的な景色を追加する。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">優れた遮音効果</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">リフトカーの構造がさらに最適化され、エレベーターは優れた遮音効果を実現し、お客様に静かで安定した使用体験を提供する。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">多様な装飾デザイン</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">昇降ドア、ハンドル、リフトカーウォールには、選択可能な一連の材料と色があり、個別にカスタマイズされたサービスを実現する。</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>半円展望エレベーター建設スケッチ</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/drawing thang k&iacute;nh tr&ograve;n - Copy.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"966\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>仕様</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang k&iacute;nh tr&ograve;n - nhật.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"536\" /></strong></p>', 1, '2023-11-08 23:36:56', '2023-11-14 23:00:08'),
(22, 9, 'Square Observation Elevator', '四角形展望エレベーター', 'square-observation-elevator', 'storage/images/product/22/1700035127016345.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Excellent car wall</strong></p>\r\n<p>It adopts highly secure, safety laminated glass. It is transparent. The passengers might appreciate the busy and prosperous city sight through the transparent car wall. The Laminated layer in laminated glass resists radiation. It buffers sound-wave vibration and isolates the sound. Large area car wall glass design shows smooth and beautiful lines. It beautifies the elevator car outline. Furthermore, the buildings are attractive.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Super wide field of view</strong></p>\r\n<p>Full transparent lift car design can maximize the field of view. Through the visual extension, passengers can have a panoramic view of all the beautiful scenery.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Multiple lift car shapes</strong></p>\r\n<p>Round,square and rhombic and other lift car shapes are optional, perfectly corresponding to different architectural styles.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Outer glass hood</strong></p>\r\n<p>It harmoniously combines with the building and surroundings. Panoramic elevator is part of the building. It also adds a mobile charming scene for the building.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Excellent sound insulation</strong></p>\r\n<p>The structure of the lift car is further optimized, which facilitates the elevator to achieve excellent sound insulation effect and customers to have quiet and steady using experience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Diverse decorative designs</strong></p>\r\n<p>There are a series of optional materials and colors for hoistway doors, handles and lift car walls, thus truly realizing individualized customized services.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Square&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><strong>O</strong>bservation Elevator Construction Sketch</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/drawing thang k&iacute;nh vu&ocirc;ng.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1038\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Specification</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang k&iacute;nh vu&ocirc;ng.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"435\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>優れたカーウォール</strong></p>\r\n<p>このウオールは安全強化ガラスを採用している。ウオール自体は透明であるので、乗客は透明なカーウォールを通じて賑やかで繁華な都市の景色を楽しむことができる。積層ガラスの中の積層層は放射線に対抗する。音波振動を緩衝し、音を遮断する効果も整えている。広いエリアのカーウォールガラスデザインは、滑らかで美しいラインを示し、エレベーターカーの輪郭を美化する。さらに、建物は魅力的である。</p>\r\n<p><strong>超広い視野</strong></p>\r\n<p>完全透明のリフトカーのデザインは、視野を最大化できる。視覚の拡張を通じて、乗客は美しい景色のパノラマビューを楽しむことができる。</p>\r\n<p><strong>複数のリフトカーの形状</strong></p>\r\n<p>円形、四角形、ひし形など、さまざまなリフトカーの形状が選択可能で、異なる建築スタイルに完璧に対応している。</p>\r\n<p><strong>外部ガラスフード</strong></p>\r\n<p>建物と周囲と調和している。パノラマエレベーターは建物の一部である。建物に移動中の魅力的な景色を追加する。</p>\r\n<p><strong>優れた遮音効果</strong></p>\r\n<p>リフトカーの構造がさらに最適化され、エレベーターは優れた遮音効果を実現し、お客様に静かで安定した使用体験を提供する。</p>\r\n<p><strong>多様な装飾デザイン</strong></p>\r\n<p>昇降ドア、ハンドル、リフトカーウォールには、選択可能な一連の材料と色があり、個別にカスタマイズされたサービスを実現する。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>広場展望エレベーター建設スケッチ</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/drawing thang k&iacute;nh vu&ocirc;ng - Copy.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1007\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>仕様</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../storage/uploads/th&ocirc;ng số thang k&iacute;nh vu&ocirc;ng nhật.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"441\" /></strong></p>', 1, '2023-11-08 23:48:58', '2023-11-14 22:58:47'),
(23, 10, 'Escalator', 'エスカレーター', 'escalator', 'storage/images/product/23/1700035053210912.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Traffic Solution Plan Specialist</strong></p>\r\n<p>It innovatively combines with human-centered ideas. It has an advanced stairway and belt design. It is smooth and comfortable in operation. Solemn and smooth handrail entry, traffic flow light appear bright and dynamic. It perfectly connects with inner/outer cover plates, skirting plate, frontline plate. It smoothly transits to a big arc rotary end handrail.</p>\r\n<p>FUJI escalators are widely applicable for the airport, railway station, high grade hotel, CBD, large-size shopping center, public facilities etc. It adds a brilliant sight line for modern buildings.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Its truss adapts the superior profile steel with unique structure, high intensity, through anti-rusting, good effect, and long life. The advanced international manufacture craft, technology, general assembly, tooling guarantee the precise elevator path.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Super-strong CPU master-board computer control executes real-time monitor to the running conditions. It automatically stops at any abnormal conditions. It also promptly and automatically makes records, displays the trouble code.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect model brings better riding experience</strong></p>\r\n<p>Extremely long life, energy efficient delivery, stable and reliable performance, will be on your right-hand man, are the best carrying tools. FUJI escalator to excellent performance, practical and flexible design to meet different customer needs. Priority use of microcomputer variable frequency(VVVF) and ergonomics research and advanced manufacturing technology, FUJI escalator is more perfect, safe, comfortable, energy-saving, and easy maintenance.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Save space with optimized design</strong></p>\r\n<p>Minimum span size greatly saves the occupied space. The compact pit depth design brings about a freer construction layout.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">交通ソリューションプランの専門家</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">この機械は革新的に人間中心のアイデアと組み合わされている。我が社のエスカレーターは高度な階段とベルトのデザインを備えており、運転は滑らかで快適である。荘厳で滑らかな手すりの入り口、明るくダイナミックな交通フローライトが明るく輝きる。このエスカレーターの内側</span><span lang=\"vi\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">/</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">外側のカバープレート、スカーティングプレート、フロントラインプレートと完璧に結びつきる。また、大きなアーチ型の回転式手すりにスムーズに移行できる。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"vi\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">FUJI</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">のエスカレーターは、空港、鉄道駅、高級ホテル、中央業務地区、大型ショッピングセンター、公共施設など、幅広い用途に適している。これは現代の建物に華やかな視線を加える。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&bull;</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"> </span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">トラスは、ユニークな構造を持つ優れた形鋼に適応し、高い強度、防錆処理、効果的な効果、長寿命を備えている。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">高度な国際製造技術、テクノロジー、総合組立、工具により、正確なエレベータ経路を保証している。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&bull;</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"> </span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">超強力な</span><span lang=\"vi\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">CPU</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">マスターボードコンピュータ制御は、運転状況のリアルタイムモニタリングを実行し、異常な状況で自動停止する。また、トラブルコードを即座に記録し、表示する。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">完璧なモデルがより良い乗車体験をもたらす</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">非常に長寿命、エネルギー効率の良いデリバリー、安定した信頼性のあるパフォーマンスは、あなたの右腕であり、最高の搬送ツールである。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"vi\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">FUJI</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">のエスカレーターは、優れたパフォーマンス、実用的で柔軟なデザインを提供し、さまざまな顧客のニーズを満たすように設計されている。マイクロコンピュータ可変周波数（</span><span lang=\"vi\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">VVVF</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">）と人間工学の研究、先進的な製造技術を優先して使用し、</span><span lang=\"vi\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Yu Mincho\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">FUJI</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">のエスカレーターはより完璧で、安全で快適でエネルギー節約で、メンテナンスが簡単である。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">最適化された設計であるペースを節約</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Yu Mincho\',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">最小のスパンサイズは、占有スペースを大幅に節約しる。コンパクトなピット深度設計により、自由な建設配置を実現する。</span></p>', 1, '2023-1